pageContext.claim: “I had a GREAT meeting with Putin and the Fake News used every bit of their energy to try and disparage it. So bad for our country!”
pageContext.analysis: There is no way to know what happened in Trump's meeting with Putin as no one was allowed in the room except their translators — even his top advisors haven't been able to confirm what was said. Since there was no further information, there was nothing else for the media to report.
